      ZERO       | ONE        | X          | Z      
ZERO  0 ^ 0 == 0 | 0 ^ 1 == 1 | 0 ^ x == x | 0 ^ z == x |
ONE   1 ^ 0 == 1 | 1 ^ 1 == 0 | 1 ^ x == x | 1 ^ z == x |
X     x ^ 0 == x | x ^ 1 == x | x ^ x == x | x ^ z == x |
Z     z ^ 0 == x | z ^ 1 == x | z ^ x == x | z ^ z == x |
